title: Kappa_Girl_12_min.mp4
description: A 12 minute long sex video of a female employee working at the Kappa store in the east building of the Shanghai No.1 Department Store on Nanjing Lu has recently been spreading like wildfire on the Chinese internet via Bittorrent and the Chinese peer-to-peer application Xunlei, catapulting the search term &#039;Kappa&#039; (or "Kappa Girl") into one of the top ten search terms on Google China and unleashing a &#039;human flesh search engine&#039; where netizens worked together to track her down, publishing her private information such as her name, her pictures and her QQ number.
